<HL>
   Law:
   Recent Rulings Give NFL Players Union
   Yardage Toward Free-Agency Goals
   ----
   By John Helyar
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/12/91
</DATE>
